prompts.frontCover: A full-body minimalist 2D illustration of the couple from the reference photo, reimagined for a humorous and sweet birthday scene. Lao Lao and Jordan are illustrated as charming cartoon characters, maintaining their poses and clothing from the photo (Lao Lao in a plain light blue sweatshirt and black pants; Jordan in a plain tan hoodie and dark pants). They are both joyfully sipping from comically oversized boba tea cups that are almost as tall as they are, with giant straws. Lao Lao looks delighted with a happy smile, while Jordan winks playfully. Little tapioca pearls float around them like festive confetti against a clean, solid off-white background. In the center of the card, written in an elegant, flowing handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday Lao Lao". The overall style is clean, modern, and minimalist, with a focus on simple shapes, flat colors, and a lighthearted, funny tone.
